{"tid":1171834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【撼頭埋牆】西環法國惡夫一手推開　29歲妻撞牆昏迷","createTime":"2019-05-26T04:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T04:02:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f21eb1615cd5a25e447f2bdeda411d8e372aac4b","tid":1171834,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190526/_2019052608334394555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190526%2F_2019052608334394555.jpg&h=d0801f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事發於美菲閣一單位。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n西環堅尼地城一對夫婦昨晚因生活問題發生爭執，36歲法國籍丈夫發惡，懷疑一手推開29歲陳姓妻子時，對方失平衡頭部撞向牆身當場昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n現場為西區士美菲路41A-43號美菲閣一單位。警方昨晚9時01分接獲保安員報案，指男子懷疑用手推其妻，女事主的頭撞向牆並受傷暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，經初步調查，兩人於寓所懷疑因生活問題爭執，男子涉嫌傷人被捕，案件交由西區警區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進。女事主頭部受傷，昏迷被送往瑪麗醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1508454/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1508454%2F&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFPno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=9984ae93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1508454%2F&h=d2450c63\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1508454/</a>"},{"pid":"0f95aaa88691d0e84715b9ccd5fa2ab3a2fe13ad","tid":1171834,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"食得洋腸抵得渴啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}